name: OcCULTFace
description:
Do you believe in shamanism? In here (IDN) this practice is quite strong in past time. But in the digital era, all these traditional things push to be digitalized. Makes the impression of creepy, mysterious, mythical is dismantled by awkwardness, fishy, and sounds like a joke.

Faces Series is an approach to translating the daily absurdity phenomenon which I've seen through social media, news, the internet, memes. And this project is all about what we consume nowadays "Written in your FACE".
